Police responded to the scene at 37 Boncker Street around 22:00 when it was reported that a gunshot had been fired.Upon arrival they found the body of a man inside a blue Opel Kadet parked at the scene.On inspection police found Mr Kaule with a single bullet wound to his head, next to his ear.He was declared dead by ER24 paramedics at the scene.A firearm with ammunition was also found at the scene and was taken in by officers from the Local Criminal Record Centre for ballistic tests.Police confirmed that Mr Kaule resided at the address.